reviewText: Loved this since I was little! Excited to know own this so I can let my kids watch this! I recommend this to anyone who has a daughter they will love this!

This is great for the little ones. Our 5 year old loves the songs and story line. Has watched it repeatedly. If you still have a VCR, this is good, clean entertainment. If you have amazon instant video, these are available there, too. You can purchase one episode, or the entire season. Found the older kids will watch this with the 5 year old. Being
enjoyed by a new generation!
